钟书阁芮欧店，上海市静安区南京西路1601号芮欧百货4层（常德路）。&lt;br pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; start=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;/&gt;
下午13点到15点。&lt;br pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; start=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;/&gt;
无主题问答唠嗑，签书。随来随看。很方便。&lt;br pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; hei=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; start=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;/&gt;
